{"id":286543,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/03/维权网-北京维权人士葛志慧要求警方公开绑架其/","date":"2013-03-29T00:16:59Z","modified":"2013-03-29T00:16:59Z","title":"维权网 | 北京维权人士葛志慧要求警方公开绑架其幼子的相关信息","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员方芳报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">28</span><span>日</span><span>，北京维权人士葛志慧通过邮局向北京市公安局丰台分局递交了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>份政府信息公开申请表，要求警方公开在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6-11</span><span>日（中共</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span><span>大期间）绑架其</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>岁儿子的相关信息，她在向公安机关递交的申请表中明确载明要求警方公开以下</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>项信息：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>、岳各庄派出所干警黄卫东将未成年人孙浩（葛志慧的儿子）带至岳各庄派出所留置、领养、调查</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>天（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>日</span><span>至</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>日</span><span>）、并禁止未成年人孙浩上学系调查案件需要、属于公务行为信息。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>、岳各庄派出所干警黄卫东将未成年人孙浩带至岳各庄派出所留置、领养、调查</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>天（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>日</span><span>至</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>日</span><span>）所涉及的案件编号（案号）信息。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>、岳各庄派出所干警黄卫东将未成年人孙浩带至岳各庄派出所留置</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>天（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>日</span><span>至</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>日</span><span>）所依据的法律法规信息。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>、岳各庄派出所干警黄卫东将未成年人孙浩带至岳各庄派出所领养</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>天（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>日</span><span>至</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>日</span><span>）所依据的法律法规信息</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>、岳各庄派出所干警黄卫东将未成年人孙浩带至岳各庄派出所调查</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>天（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>日</span><span>至</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>日</span><span>）行为所依据的法律法规信息。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>、岳各庄派出所干警黄卫东将未成年人孙浩带至岳各庄派出所禁止其上学所依据的法律法规信息。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>、岳各庄派出所干警黄卫东传唤、留置、拘留未成年人孙浩</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>天（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>日</span><span>至</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>日</span><span>）所制作、获取的包括传唤证、拘留证、逮捕证在内但不局限于传唤证、拘留证、逮捕证所有合法手续信息。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>、</span><span> </span><span>岳各庄派出所干警黄卫东传唤、留置、拘留未成年人孙浩</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>天（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>日</span><span>至</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>日</span><span>）内制作、获取的所有笔录信息。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>、岳各庄派出所干警黄卫东传唤、留置、拘留未成年人孙浩</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>天（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>日</span><span>至</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>日</span><span>）内制作、获取的所有摄像资料信息。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>、岳各庄派出所干警黄卫东传唤、留置、拘留未成年人孙浩</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>天（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>日</span><span>至</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>日</span><span>）后所做的最终调查结论信息。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>、岳各庄派出所干警黄卫东拘留、逮捕未成年人孙浩</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>天（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>日</span><span>至</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>日</span><span>）后释放孙浩的释放证信息。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>葛志慧是北京市丰台区政府官商勾结野蛮暴力强拆的受害人，两年前因反抗违法强拆被殴打致残，财产被抢劫一空，至今未做任何补偿和安置。两年来，葛志慧流离失所不屈不挠拖着残疾的身体一直奔波在艰难的上访维权路上。被强拆和掠夺的财产赔偿问题不但没有解决反而被北京市丰台区政府列为重点维稳对象，多次被拘留、软禁和关黑监狱，每到“敏感日子”都被严密监控禁止外出，临时居住的楼道口安装了监控摄像头。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span><span>中共</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span><span>大召开前夕</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span><span>，葛志慧为避免被再次关进黑监狱受迫害，她设法逃离监控躲藏在外。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>日</span><span>，负责稳控葛志慧的北京市丰台区公安局岳各庄派出所的副所长黄卫东带领几名干警公然闯到葛志慧前夫家抄家并抓走他的前夫，将葛志慧正在上小学</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>年级的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>岁儿子绑架到派出所非法关押</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>天，期间让孩子“交代”葛志慧的行踪。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>日</span><span>，葛志慧被丰台区警方抓捕，以莫须有的“聚众扰乱社会秩序”罪关押在丰台区看守所</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">40</span><span>天，现在仍在取保候审中。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>葛志慧</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>岁的儿子亲眼目睹爸爸被警察带上手铐铐在酷刑椅子上的情景，孩子当时被吓懵了。之后连续</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>天在派出所警察一直在逼问他关于葛志慧的有关事情，孩子受到了严重的惊吓。谈起当时的情形，葛志慧的儿子至今还惊恐万分，他说：“当时我以为他们要枪毙我爸爸，我可害怕了。他们给我饭我也不敢吃，我怕里面有毒！”</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>回家后受到严重惊吓的孩子得了自闭症，成天躲在屋里不敢出来一直喊着要妈妈，两个多月一直不敢出门去上学，至今只要一见到警车和警察就惊慌失措，直到现在妈妈不在身边陪着晚上浩浩一个人不敢睡觉。葛志慧的儿子浩浩原本是个活泼、可爱、健谈、爱好学习的孩子，虽然葛志慧千方百计已经让孩子恢复上学，但现在孩子很少和外人交谈也不愿学习。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>葛志慧：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13261499836</span></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[16910]}